{"tid":1842641,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"認為肺炎攬炒論有誤","createTime":"2020-01-25T20:41:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T21:47:09.000Z","uid":147721,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"29e51371aaa9e61697511de969a95b1e9d84d5e7","tid":1842641,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T20:41:11.000Z","msg":"本身攬炒論既本質 係game of chicken既策略<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/膽小鬼博弈\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-tw%2F%E8%86%BD%E5%B0%8F%E9%AC%BC%E5%8D%9A%E5%BC%88&d=DF3UGDbnXTwcWfCLvBafJWa%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=7b90310b\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/膽小鬼博弈</a><br />\n係展現我地唔怕攬炒 展現一係支共轉彎一係撞車 從而迫支共選擇轉彎<br />\n當然除左策略性迫支共轉彎外 亦都有少量意氣因素<br />\n但正正就係呢個意氣因素 令攬炒策略係支共睇黎有可信性<br />\n<br />\n而肺炎黎講 已經唔係game of chicken 因為病毒話之你港人定支共 都係咁樣傳染同殺人<br />\n所以<strong><ins>我地唔應該懶懶閒咁話 用肺炎同支共一齊攬炒<br />\n而係努力自救 留返條命旁觀支爆</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n香港人 洗手<br />\n香港人 戴口罩<br />\n香港人 消毒<br />\n香港人 封關<br />\n香港人 自救"},{"pid":"c35e8b53e842f53b60be75b0024fdc3dbdf2496f","tid":1842641,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T20:57:51.000Z","msg":"【寧為玉碎 不作瓦全】黃台仰2020年同大家講話<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1842621\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1842621</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cff24ea8ea4107cd601a18ed960783afc68313df","tid":1842641,"uid":66099,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T21:27:17.000Z","msg":"死咪死"},{"pid":"5398129aabe0c3552c905a6973f621e1787f30df","tid":1842641,"uid":92353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T21:47:09.000Z","msg":"肺炎攬炒論係基於死亡率年齡分佈<br />\n老人死亡率高好多"}]}